    "status" : "extensions",
    "div" : "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet tiflow-chargeitem-operation-outcome-details-vs</b></p><a name=\"tiflow-chargeitem-operation-outcome-details-vs\"> </a><a name=\"hctiflow-chargeitem-operation-outcome-details-vs\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include all codes defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-tiflow-chargeitem-operation-outcome-details-cs.html\"><code>https://gematik.de/fhir/tiflow/chargeitem/CodeSystem/tiflow-chargeitem-operation-outcome-details-cs</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version &#x1F4E6;1.0.0-draft</span></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html\"><code>https://gematik.de/fhir/tiflow/core/CodeSystem/tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version &#x1F4E6;1.0.0-draft</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_AUTH_ROLE_NOT_ALLOWED\">TIFLOW_AUTH_ROLE_NOT_ALLOWED</a></td><td>Access role not allowed</td><td>The authenticated actor role is not permitted to execute this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_CONSENT_ALREADY_EXISTS\">TIFLOW_CONSENT_ALREADY_EXISTS</a></td><td>Consent already exists</td><td>A consent for the same scope already exists and cannot be created again</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_CONSENT_CATEGORY_REQUIRED\">TIFLOW_CONSENT_CATEGORY_REQUIRED</a></td><td>Consent category required</td><td>The consent category is mandatory and was not provided</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_CONSENT_CATEGORY_INVALID\">TIFLOW_CONSENT_CATEGORY_INVALID</a></td><td>Consent category invalid</td><td>The provided consent category is unknown or not allowed</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_ACCESSCODE_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_ACCESSCODE_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Access code mismatch</td><td>The provided access code does not match the access code assigned to the task</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_TASK_REQUIRED\">TIFLOW_TASK_REQUIRED</a></td><td>Task required</td><td>A task reference is required for this operation but was not provided</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_TASK_NOT_FOUND\">TIFLOW_TASK_NOT_FOUND</a></td><td>Task not found</td><td>The referenced task does not exist</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_SECRET_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_SECRET_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Task secret mismatch</td><td>The provided task secret does not match the secret stored for the task</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_CONSENT_REQUIRED\">TIFLOW_CONSENT_REQUIRED</a></td><td>Consent required</td><td>A valid consent is required to execute this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_OCSP_BACKEND_ERROR\">TIFLOW_OCSP_BACKEND_ERROR</a></td><td>Invalid OCSP response</td><td>Failed to retrieve the OCSP response for the certificate of the signature</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_MESSAGE_TO_SELF\">TIFLOW_MESSAGE_TO_SELF</a></td><td>Message to self not allowed</td><td>A communication message addressed to the sender itself is not permitted</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_COMMUNICATION_PAYLOAD_INVALID\">TIFLOW_COMMUNICATION_PAYLOAD_INVALID</a></td><td>Communication payload invalid</td><td>The communication payload is syntactically or semantically invalid</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_INSURANT_NOT_ELIGIBLE\">TIFLOW_INSURANT_NOT_ELIGIBLE</a></td><td>Insurant not eligible</td><td>The insurant does not meet the eligibility constraints for this communication flow</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_RECIPIENT_INVALID\">TIFLOW_RECIPIENT_INVALID</a></td><td>Recipient invalid</td><td>The specified recipient is invalid for the requested communication</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_TASK_STATUS_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_TASK_STATUS_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Task status mismatch</td><td>The task is in a status that does not allow execution of this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_TASK_EXPIRED\">TIFLOW_TASK_EXPIRED</a></td><td>Task expired</td><td>The task cannot be processed because its redemption period has expired</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_MVO_NOT_VALID_YET\">TIFLOW_MVO_NOT_VALID_YET</a></td><td>MVO not valid yet</td><td>The multi-prescription is not yet valid at the current point in time</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"https://simplifier.net/resolve?scope=de.gematik.epa.medication@1.3.0&amp;canonical=https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes\"><code>https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to 1.1.1, the version found through the package references\"> version &#x1F4E6;1.1.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://simplifier.net/resolve?scope=de.gematik.epa.medication@1.3.0&amp;canonical=https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes#operation-outcome-details-codes-SVC_IDENTITY_MISMATCH\">SVC_IDENTITY_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Identity mismatch: Access token or x-insurantid header does not match FHIR data (Telematik-ID / KVNR)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://simplifier.net/resolve?scope=de.gematik.epa.medication@1.3.0&amp;canonical=https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes#operation-outcome-details-codes-SVC_VALIDATION_FAILED\">SVC_VALIDATION_FAILED</a></td><td>FHIR Profile Validation Failed</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
